data.description: A slice of Texas heaven on 2 acres in beautiful Floresville, TX. Time to start building memories in this home that's just down the road from all this charming town has to offer yet feels tucked away.  Open floorplan w/ 10' ceilings and not a stitch of carpeting. Pass through your Florida room into your welcoming and ample living area. Kitchen has a HUGE pantry and plenty of countertop for food prep. Peer out onto your covered backyard patio from your kitchen window at 2 producing pear trees and 1 fig tree! Property possesses a capped well for future irrigation if desired. Each bedroom has its own ceiling fan and closet. This home has a large, functional laundry room complete with sink. Super-sized garage boasts many additional electrical outlets and an added storage room...not to mention attic storage! HVAC recently serviced. Home freshly interior freshly painted, was leveled in 3/23 and its Septic pumped 7/22.
